snippet: The United States beat New Zealand for the first time in the World Rugby Sevens series, winning by 14-12 to reach the quarterfinals in Dubai, United Arab Emirates, on points difference.
abstract: United States reaches quarterfinals of World Rugby Sevens series, beating New Zealand for first time, 14-12.
lead_paragraph: The United States beat New Zealand for the first time in the World Rugby Sevens series, winning by 14-12 to reach the quarterfinals in Dubai, United Arab Emirates, on points difference.
